# candidate outputs are graded artifacts, never committed
tasks/*/output/
# graded-run records: runs/<suite>/<candidate>-<date>/ is a COMMITTED durable home —
# RESULTS doc + runner + per-rep {config.json, verdicts/, responses/, grade.txt}. These are
# small (the coach-heldout first record is ~0.5 MB), fully pinned (model/quant/template/SHAs)
# and auditable, so they are tracked. Convention set by the first record (runs/coach-heldout/,
# 2026-07-09). Exclude only heavyweight raw dumps if a future suite produces them:
# runs/**/responses/*.bin  (none today)

